+# API Endpoint Coverage (Progress: 55/55)
+Legend: [ ] not yet tested  -  [x] test written and passing  -  [~] intentionally skipped (reason)
+
+## RegistryAPI (server/src/main/java/org/eclipse/openvsx/RegistryAPI.java)
+- [x] GET /api/{namespace} - namespace metadata, 404 if not found
+- [x] GET /api/{namespace}/verify-pat - verify PAT token, 400/404 on error
+- [x] GET /api/{namespace}/details - namespace details, 404 if not found
+- [x] GET /api/{namespace}/logo/{fileName} - namespace logo image, 404 if not found
+- [x] GET /api/{namespace}/{extension} - latest extension metadata, 404 if not found
+- [x] GET /api/{namespace}/{extension}/{targetPlatform} - latest for platform, 404 if not found
+- [x] GET /api/{namespace}/{extension}/{version} - specific version metadata, 404 if not found
+- [x] GET /api/{namespace}/{extension}/{targetPlatform}/{version} - specific version for platform, 404 if not found
+- [x] GET /api/{namespace}/{extension}/versions - paginated version list, 400 on negative params
